      <div class="detail">
        <p>20-Point <br /> Infrared Touch</p>
        <span>Interaction</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>3840 x 2160 <br /> (4K)</p>
        <span> Resolution </span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Directional 8-Mic <br /> Voice Module</p>
        <span> AI Voice</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <Image class={"blue-shade"} src={blue_shade} alt={""} format="webp" />
  </section>

  <section id="points-section">
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="media"
    >
      <source src="/videos/holographic/1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="points">
      <div class="point">
        <p class="subtitle-2">High-Performance Computing Core</p>
        <span class="paragraph-2">
          The system is powered by a robust standard configuration: RK3588
          processor with 8GB of RAM and 128GB of storage. This high-performance
          core ensures smooth, real-time rendering of the 4K digital human
          avatar and rapid processing of voice and touch inputs, providing a
          fluid and lag-free user experience.
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="point">
        <p class="subtitle-2">Immersive 4K Transparent Display</p>
        <span class="paragraph-2">
          The centerpiece of the YC-T86X75 is its stunning 75-inch Ultra HD
          transparent LCD screen. With a resolution of 3840 x 2160 (4K), it
          delivers crystal-clear visuals for the digital human avatar,
          seamlessly blending the virtual with the real world. The transparent
          nature of the screen allows for unique retail and exhibition
          applications where physical products can be showcased behind the
          digital host.
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="point">
        <p class="subtitle-2">Elegant and Patented Design</p>
        <span class="paragraph-2">
          The YC-T86X75 features a sleek, floor-standing design with an
          appearance patent, making it a premium fixture for any modern space.
          The built-in stereo speakers complement the visual experience,
          ensuring high-quality audio output for the digital human's voice and
          multimedia content.
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="point">
        <p class="subtitle-2">Advanced AI-Powered Interaction</p>
        <span class="paragraph-2">
          This cabinet is built for intuitive human-computer interaction. It
          features a highly sensitive 20-point infrared touch capability,
          allowing users to interact directly with the digital human and
          displayed content. For voice interaction, a Directional 8-mic
          dedicated voice module with noise reduction is integrated, ensuring
          clear communication and a natural dialogue experience.
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="tech-section">
    <!-- <Picture src={specs} alt={"Technical specifications"} /> -->

    <div class="table">
      <div class="head">
        <div class="line-element big-desktop">
          <div></div>
          <span> rYC-T86X751 </span>
          <div></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="h1">Technical Specifications</h2>
      </div>

